      "versionNonce": 1,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Signal Detection  (2-pass)\n\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\nPass 1 \u2014 keyword rules (free, fast):\n  semver \u2192 SIGNAL  \u2022  gh-release \u2192 SIGNAL\n  tracked-acct reply \u2192 CANDIDATE\nPass 2 \u2014 LLM classifier:\n  CENTRALIZED: OpenRouter API  (Gemini Flash free / Claude Haiku paid)\n  DISTRIBUTED: user's local 'claude -p' or 'codex' CLI  (zero extra cost)\nOutput: SIGNAL | CONTEXT | NOISE",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "signal",
      "originalText": "Signal Detection  (2-pass)\n\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\nPass 1 \u2014 keyword rules (free, fast):\n  semver \u2192 SIGNAL  \u2022  gh-release \u2192 SIGNAL\n  tracked-acct reply \u2192 CANDIDATE\nPass 2 \u2014 LLM classifier:\n  CENTRALIZED: OpenRouter API  (Gemini Flash free / Claude Haiku paid)\n  DISTRIBUTED: user's local 'claude -p' or 'codex' CLI  (zero extra cost)\nOutput: SIGNAL | CONTEXT | NOISE",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.4
    },
